Package com.example.flexiMed.dto

Class ServiceHistoryDTO

java.lang.Object
com.example.flexiMed.dto.ServiceHistoryDTO
public class ServiceHistoryDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for representing a service history record in the system. It includes details about the service event associated with a request.
